## File-specific overrides
| Location | Special rules |
|----------|---------------|
| `lib/**` | Console allowed, looser unused vars |
| `scripts/**` | Console allowed, no-var-requires off |
| `tests/**` | Console allowed, looser rules |
| `functions/**` | Console allowed |
| `app/**` | Console allowed |
| `components/**` | Console allowed |

## Running lint
```bash
npm run lint           # Check all files
npm run lint -- --fix  # Auto-fix issues
```
